		<history>
			<header>Early history</header>
			<text>From 2011 to the end of 2013, Svenardo.com produced HTML5 javascript games meant to be played in the browser. Some of the more notable games produced in this era are Jetman Jr, 8-bit Carnage and Realtime Chess, both which landed considerable acclaim and picked up a lot of interest.</text>
